Camoflage::

She carried the little bot into the mess hall and sat her down in a 
chair. "OOfff,gosh your heavy. My arms are tired from carrying you 
around. Does your mommy know how big you are? If she doesn't, then 
I'll let her know. Your almost too big for me to carry." as she tried 
to sound like a bigger bot herself.  She went to the machine and 
ordered Elita something nice to eat. Fresh sweet creamed energon with 
strawberries and served up her new friend. "OK, after this, we can go 
back to your room and wait for your mommy to get back." She  She 
smiled at Elita and rubbed her ears.  She turned form the table for a 
minute and let her own tummy grumble a bit. She didn't want to eat 
anything until Elita was finished. To her, somewhere in her programs, 
her responibillities came first. "Eat up, then we can go back."
